    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Primary total hip or knee arthroplasty

          -  Age 55 to 75 years

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Deficient written or spoken danish

          -  Alcohol abuse (&gt;21 U per week)

          -  Immunocompromised

          -  Anticoagulant therapy

          -  ASA class 4-5

          -  Functional impairment from psychological or neurological disease

          -  Sleepapnea
      </textblock>
